ness.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"This is practiced by the majority of scholars, that it is recommended\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20465,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/13\/tongue-deserves-imprisonment\/","url_meta":{"origin":33999,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas&#8217;ud on Silence: Nothing deserves jail like the tongue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Anbas ibn 'Uqbah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas'ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"By Allah, besides whom there is no God, nothing on earth is in greater need of a lengthy prison sentence than the tongue.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 8745 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0633\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35053,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/25\/good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33999,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Dua: Goodness is knowledge in world, Paradise in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn Hassan reported: Al-Hasan, may Allah have mercy on him, said in regards to His saying, \u201cO Lord, give us good in the world and good in the Hereafter,\u201d (2:201) that good in the world is knowledge and worship, and good in the Hereafter is Paradise. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32697,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/06\/scholars-with-ignorant-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":33999,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: The Prophet fears scholars with ignorant hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among what I fear most for my nation is every hypocrite with a knowledgeable tongue.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 140 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18222,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/20\/seeking-knowledge-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":33999,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Seeking knowledge is jihad in way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoev